I'm an introvert and not really talkative. I also haven't even been active on Twitter these days cuz of working on multiple jobs and streaming but I still enjoy a good conversation related to video games and anime so you may see me respond here and there. [4]

Aside from gaming, I watch anime or read manga and when I'm feeling creative, I like to write stories and draw some of my favorite characters (I'm a bit rusty now). I've been doing some photo & video editing and I hope to learn more so I could edit my own VODs soon. [3]
